OL,3,CMPs urge new Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,4,Cto scrap #100m slavery reparations plan
OL,6,FA group of MPs and peers have urged
OL,7,Fthe the incoming Archbishop of
OL,8,FCanterbury to stop the Church of
OL,9,FEngland from spending #100 million on
OL,10,Fslavery reparations.
OL,12,FThe 27 parliamentarians warn in a
OL,13,Fletter to Dame Sarah Mullally that the
OL,14,Fmove could set a "worrying precedent"
OL,15,Ffor other organisations to feel they
OL,16,Fmust follow suit.
