OL,3,CMPs urge new Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,4,Cto scrap #100m slavery reparations plan
OL,6,FThe plan is for #100 million from the
OL,7,FChurch Commissioners endowment to go
OL,8,Finto a separate charitable fund for
OL,9,F"healing, repair and justice" that
OL,10,Fwill grow over time and be used to
OL,11,Finvest in support for historically
OL,12,Fmarginalised groups, in particular
OL,13,Fcommunities affected by historic
OL,14,FAfrican chattel enslavement.
OL,16,FThe parliamentarians say the endowment
OL,17,Fby law is supposed to be used to
OL,18,Fsupport parish ministry, maintain
OL,19,Fchurch buildings, and care for the
OL,20,FChurch's historic records.
