OL,3,CMPs urge new Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,4,Cto scrap #100m slavery reparations plan
OL,6,F"At a moment when churches across the
OL,7,Fcountry are struggling to keep their
OL,8,Fdoors open ` many even falling into
OL,9,Fdisrepair ` it's wrong to try and
OL,10,Fjustify diverting #100 million to a
OL,11,Fproject entirely separate from those
OL,12,Fcore obligations," the letter reads.
OL,14,FThe group, led by shadow Home Office
OL,15,Fminister Katie Lam and with
OL,16,Fsignatories including senior
OL,17,FConservatives Chris Philp, Claire
OL,18,FCoutinho and Neil O'Brien, also
OL,19,Fquestions the "evidential basis" of
OL,20,Fthe plan known as Project Spire.
