OL,3,CMPs urge new Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,4,Cto scrap #100m slavery reparations plan
OL,6,FThe project was launched after the
OL,7,FChurch carried out research into the
OL,8,Fhistorical links to slavery of its
OL,9,Fendowment.
OL,11,F"The Church has a long and complex
OL,12,Fhistorical record, one that includes
OL,13,Fboth moral failures and courageous
OL,14,Fleadership in the abolitionist
OL,15,Fmovement.
OL,17,F"To reduce this history to a
OL,18,Fsimplistic narrative of guilt does a
OL,19,Fdisservice both to truth and to the
OL,20,FChurch's own legacy," the letter adds.
