OL,6,FThe group makes its appeal to Dame
OL,7,FSarah as she is due to be legally made
OL,8,FArchbishop of Canterbury in January.
OL,10,FThey write: "A clear signal from you
OL,11,Fnow that the focus of the Church under
OL,12,Fyour leadership will be the
OL,13,Fstrengthening of parishes, not the
OL,14,Fpursuit of high-profile and legally
OL,15,Fdubious vanity projects, would
OL,16,Freassure the many worshippers, clergy,
OL,17,Fand members of the public who have
OL,18,Fcontacted us with their concerns."
